    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "To do list:\n\nPlayer:\nV  - Double jump\r\nV  - Jump height/time based
    on how long you hold the spacebar\r\nV  - Coyote time (post-ground grace period
    for jumping)\r\nV  - Jump buffering (pre-ground input forgiveness)\nV  - Shrink
    player over time\nV  - make jump and movement scale with size\nV  - make objects
    heavyer with size\n    - make objects feel heavyer with size\n\nGameplay:\nV 
    - Pickup objects\n    - open cabinets and drawers\n    - interact with equipment
    when holding potion\n    - show floating UI when hovering over something like
    potions and equipment\n    - make potions and recipies spawn in random set locations\n   
    - Set text on objects like wall or object pickup\n    - keep track of how many
    of the ingridients the player has found\n\nUI:\n    - Main menu\n    - Level
    select\n    - Settings\n    - lose screen\n    - pause screen that also pauses
    the game\n    - Win screen\n\nJuice:\n    - Sound:\n        - Background music\n       
    - footsteps\n        - collition\n        - Equipment interaction\n        -
    Equipment complete\n        - Drawers and cabenets\n    - Particles\n    - Animations\n   
    - \n    - \n\n"
